{"tid":1352643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去元朗唱聖詩招降 有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-07-22T22:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T10:10:06.000Z","uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b949285707f0c92f80e158ddfda28a6797eb8023","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:11:43.000Z","msg":"如果去唱聖詩都被人打 國際關注一定更大 <br />\n加上依家風頭火勢 警犬冇咁易由得班仆街亂嚟"},{"pid":"30afe39b0e78526b68f7c8f15578964b8a358b4c","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:14:10.000Z","msg":"依家某程度上都係一個局嚟<br />\n<br />\n你去打佢哋 就會用不同刑事罪名拉曬勇武勢力<br />\n你唔打佢哋 就會由佢哋佔上風 以後要被佢哋用黑幫威脅你示威<br />\n<br />\n係打同唔打都會死嘅情況下<br />\n係咪應該要尋求第三條出路？"},{"pid":"4dc6eaea1138299b4ec02e1067c856b9c9b9ca41","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:15:58.000Z","msg":"當大家都糾結係打定唔打嘅時候<br />\n或者應該抽身 諗下有冇更加好嘅方法"},{"pid":"46a001629194e1a2881ecb34e5fc84aef6cc5a7d","tid":1352643,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:16:12.000Z","msg":"我地應該將光復元朗當成遍地開花其中一部份<br />\n<br />\n係元朗聚焦返５＋１大訴求<br />\n１。全面撤回送中<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗暴動<br />\n<br />\n光復元朗正確方向！！７２７元朗反送中Ｘ反警黑！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1352523/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1352523/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"128408fa0cb9ffa2279a2dd7b6f01a305d7cbc16","tid":1352643,"uid":167828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:16:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a1ca034be2ce97e0bef44b7eb9d18f83f34c545","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"128408fa0cb9ffa2279a2dd7b6f01a305d7cbc16","tid":1352643,"uid":167828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:16:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:19:37.000Z","msg":"我自己睇件事就係香港政府set嘅兩難陷阱嚟<br />\n依家會將件事定性為不同政見人士嘅私鬥<br />\n可以一次過出師有名拉曬所有勇武勢力<br />\n但我認同 一日唔光復 一日都會被人捉住個春袋嚟做人<br />\n市民活係恐懼之中 更加不利日後動員人出嚟<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好被人帶風向 執著係只得打同唔打呢兩個option上"},{"pid":"dbb127dc2c68c5517527361eec9671dbac801d8e","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:22:44.000Z","msg":"我再推"},{"pid":"6b7719c6b25493d40e8df56097ba304fc9733c0a","tid":1352643,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:24:33.000Z","msg":"和理非元朗，勇武西環<br />\n和理非元朗可以突顯警黑暴力，勇武手足唔使送頭。<br />\n勇武西環可以迅速令局勢升温"},{"pid":"31b3ba2be0a6281693d2964d6563b5074dd6cf46","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:30:38.000Z","msg":"我唔係想叫人唔好光復 亦唔係和理非理念<br />\n而係希望大家冷靜去睇件事<br />\n<br />\n一 畀你光復成功 只係挫一挫佢哋銳氣 要從此滅絕黑社會係冇可能嘅事<br />\n二 無論成唔成功都必然有義士受傷 被拉 而且因為冇政治包袱 警犬可以做得比之前更加狠 更加狼 啱曬佢心意去拉曬最勇武嘅勢力<br />\n三 一旦失敗損失慘重 軍心大亂 人心惶惶 以後好難再動員更加多嘅人出去示威<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係 光復係必須要做嘅事 點解我覺得唱聖詩可以考慮<br />\n一 唔可以亂咁拉同攻擊搞宗教活動嘅人 係同私鬥完全唔同性質 國際關注會高好多<br />\n二 相信經過六月大家都知洗腦式唱聖詩係ok work<br />\n三 如果唱聖詩被打 先再自衛 件事都可以完全唔同包裝"},{"pid":"b622182f6eb43be1a11e9a7055eacf2b4e3b873e","tid":1352643,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:32:00.000Z","msg":"秋天快到 安全第一<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小心山火</span></span>"},{"pid":"be522766348d4b62adfb6657287272e5d362117b","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:34:20.000Z","msg":"外面風向一直引導大家思考只走兩條路<br />\n<br />\n「打死班人 就算被人拉曬去坐監都要打」<br />\n「唔好去呀 好危險呀 會送死」<br />\n<br />\n而兩個結果都會係政府贏嘅局面<br />\n大家要冷靜啲"},{"pid":"9d3e93ada3ad337414effc7ccf7125499bfc5349","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b3b13b59b88f50f55d8547828c1aee19618297","tid":1352643,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:37:59.000Z","msg":"係好既<br />\n但我旬係送教徙去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b12eac871d8c2b23002e53d56c88779a9c2d12f","tid":1352643,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65b3b13b59b88f50f55d8547828c1aee19618297","tid":1352643,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:37:59.000Z","msg":"係好既<br />\n但我旬係送教徙去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:38:09.000Z","msg":"怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa83158133481c8b3a86faa8efff141cba4da328","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b12eac871d8c2b23002e53d56c88779a9c2d12f","tid":1352643,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65b3b13b59b88f50f55d8547828c1aee19618297","tid":1352643,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:37:59.000Z","msg":"係好既<br />\n但我旬係送教徙去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:38:09.000Z","msg":"怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:40:01.000Z","msg":"人人都可以唱聖詩 唔需要擺教徒上檯要佢哋送頭<br />\n<br />\n而搞示威者同搞宗教人士係兩個性質嚟 <br />\n就算之後要自衛再打 都有得包裝 唔會被政府定性你係私鬥"},{"pid":"2199852f8522ead790ab4242c797659267f32c70","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:41:54.000Z","msg":"好多人負評想個post沉底<br />\n但冇人討論過第三個方法<br />\n唔一定要唱聖詩 但我覺得都唔需要拘泥於「打」同「唔打」兩者上面"},{"pid":"1609e62f4ba39bcadc1f9e9fa0235855fcead0e5","tid":1352643,"uid":277551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:44:01.000Z","msg":"Sorry 不敢苟同<br />\n依家係焦土派出動時間<br />\n我撐隻妖嫁！最好就18區打到戒嚴<br />\n打撚醒班沉睡港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔係想有人受傷<br />\n但始終人覺醒最快途徑就係影響自己既利益<br />\n<br />\n落街無送買。行街無舖開。食飯無飯食。<br />\n總之一定要從第三方影響民生就會有更多人加入我地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n犬唔執法就會減少支持率！俾班藍絲知道佢地係水深火熱之中！<br />\n<br />\n太執法既都只不過係黑吃黑，無傷大雅。<br />\n交人都無所謂，戲做足又點？大家會信咩？<br />\n<br />\n總之一個字！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遍地開花！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"31e31699b738d3f147fd14ecfc6201ce0fedae34","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:03:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818fd2d90a9e19140f195a1edbbdc7a20f97e851","tid":1352643,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:10:06.000Z","msg":"元朗星期六有宗教集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364035\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364035</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊撚個負評我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}